sentences_data.text: Land our highest variable rate on Savings Accelerator.

ING DIRECT Savings Accelerator With one of the strongest variable savings rates in the country on balances of $150,000 or more - and zero ING DIRECT fees - Savings Accelerator helps bring your investing goals closer.

2.35% - Great ongoing variable rate Easy access to your money when you need it No penalties for making regular or one-off withdrawals Ongoing variable rate on $150,000+ balances Get a stronger return on your investment Open Savings Accelerator at ingdirect.com.au Or call 1800 103 657-our Australia-based savings specialists are here 24/7.
ING DIRECT How banking can be For the curious: Information and interest rates are current as at 22 March 2017 and are subject to change.
Any advice in this advertisement does not take into account your objectives, financial situation or needs and you should consider whether it is appropriate for you.
With Savings Accelerator, a different variable interest rate applies depending on the total balance: 2.35% p.a.
if total balance is $150,000 or over 1.75% p.a.
if total balance is $50,000 to $149,999.99;1.50% pa iftotal balance is under $50,000.
Read the Savings Accelerator Terms and Conditions available at inqdirectcom.au and consider if this product is right for you.
